## Modules

Modules are reusable collections of Terraform configurations.

### Advantages

* Code reusability
* Standardized deployments
* Improved maintainability
* Better project organization

### Types of Modules

#### Root Module

The main configuration executed by Terraform.

#### Child Module

Reusable module called by another module.

#### Registry Module

Pre-built module downloaded from Terraform Registry.

